<!-- ServiceModals.astro – Pop-up modaler för Technology & Systems OCH Retail Optimization -->

<!-- ═══ MODAL: Video Analytics & Heatmapping ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-video-heatmap">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('video-heatmap')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2>Video Analytics &amp; Heatmapping</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Förvandla ditt befintliga CCTV-system till ett kraftfullt analysverktyg. Vår lösning är kompatibel med alla kameraplattformar vi testat – ingen ny hårdvara krävs.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">Turn your existing CCTV system into a powerful analytics tool. Compatible with all camera platforms we have tested – no new hardware required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/heatmap-store.jpg" alt="Store heatmap" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>heatmap-store.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/cctv-retail.jpg" alt="CCTV retail camera" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>cctv-retail.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kompatibelt med alla CCTV-system</strong><strong class="en-text">Compatible with all CCTV systems</strong><span class="sv-text">Koppla på vår analysmodul mot din befintliga infrastruktur – AXIS, Hanwha, Hikvision m.fl.</span><span class="en-text">Connect our analytics module to your existing infrastructure – AXIS, Hanwha, Hikvision and more.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Varma och kalla zoner</strong><strong class="en-text">Hot and cold zones</strong><span class="sv-text">Se tydligt vilka delar av butiken som attraherar flest kunder och vilka ytor som underprestererar.</span><span class="en-text">See clearly which parts of the store attract the most customers and which areas underperform.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Realtidsanalys och trender</strong><strong class="en-text">Real-time analysis and trends</strong><span class="sv-text">Följ kundflöden live eller analysera rörelsemönster över tid – per veckodag, kampanjperiod eller säsong.</span><span class="en-text">Monitor customer flows live or analyze movement patterns over time – by weekday, campaign period or season.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Flöden och genvägar</strong><strong class="en-text">Flows and shortcuts</strong><span class="sv-text">Identifiera vilka rutter kunderna tar, var de stannar upp och var de passerar utan att engagera sig.</span><span class="en-text">Identify which routes customers take, where they stop and where they pass without engaging.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Intryck och besökstid</strong><strong class="en-text">Impressions and dwell time</strong><span class="sv-text">Mät genomsnittlig besökstid per zon och se vilka exponeringsytor som skapar verklig uppmärksamhet.</span><span class="en-text">Measure average dwell time per zone and see which display areas generate real attention.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Mobil dashboard</strong><strong class="en-text">Mobile dashboard</strong><span class="sv-text">Åtkomst till heatmaps och nyckeltal direkt i mobilen – för butikschefen i farten.</span><span class="en-text">Access heatmaps and KPIs directly on mobile – for the store manager on the go.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4–15%</strong><span class="sv-text">försäljningsväxt</span><span class="en-text">sales growth</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>80+</strong><span class="sv-text">genomförda projekt</span><span class="en-text">completed projects</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Alla CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">All CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">kompatibelt</span><span class="en-text">compatible</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ MODAL: Video Shelf Analytics ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-video-shelf-analytics">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('video-shelf-analytics')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2>Video Shelf Analytics</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Förstå exakt vilka hyllor, gavlar och störtar som är butikens mest attraktiva placeringar. Vår AI-modell tolkar din butiksritning och mappar ut alla zoner automatiskt.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">Understand exactly which shelves, end caps and dump bins are your store's most attractive placements. Our AI model interprets your store sketch and maps all zones automatically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/storesketch.jpg" alt="Store sketch zone mapping" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>storesketch.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/shelf-heatmap.jpg" alt="Shelf heatmap" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>shelf-heatmap.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Automatisk zonmappning</strong><strong class="en-text">Automatic zone mapping</strong><span class="sv-text">Ladda upp din butiksritning. Vår AI identifierar automatiskt alla hyllsektioner, gavlar och störtar.</span><span class="en-text">Upload your store sketch. Our AI automatically identifies all shelf sections, end caps and dump bins.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Varma och kalla hyllzoner</strong><strong class="en-text">Hot and cold shelf zones</strong><span class="sv-text">Se exakt var kunderna stannar upp och engagerar sig – och vilka hyllsektioner som passeras utan uppmärksamhet.</span><span class="en-text">See exactly where customers stop and engage – and which shelf sections are passed without attention.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Optimal produktplacering</strong><strong class="en-text">Optimal product placement</strong><span class="sv-text">Kombinera hyllanalys med försäljningsdata (POS) för att identifiera vilka produkter som bör exponeras var.</span><span class="en-text">Combine shelf analytics with sales data (POS) to identify which products should be placed where.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Gavlar och störtar</strong><strong class="en-text">End caps and dump bins</strong><span class="sv-text">Identifiera dina mest premium-exponeringsytor med faktiska besöksdata som beslutsunderlag.</span><span class="en-text">Identify your most premium display spaces with real visitor data as the basis for decisions.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kompatibelt med befintlig CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">Compatible with existing CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">Inget behov av ny hårdvara – systemet integreras mot din befintliga kamerainfrastruktur.</span><span class="en-text">No need for new hardware – the system integrates with your existing camera infrastructure.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Trendanalys</strong><strong class="en-text">Trend analysis</strong><span class="sv-text">Jämför hyllzonernas prestation under kampanjperioder mot normaltrafik och optimera löpande.</span><span class="en-text">Compare shelf zone performance during campaign periods against normal traffic and optimize continuously.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4–15%</strong><span class="sv-text">försäljningsväxt</span><span class="en-text">sales growth</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>AI-driven</strong><span class="sv-text">zonmappning</span><span class="en-text">zone mapping</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Alla CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">All CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">kompatibelt</span><span class="en-text">compatible</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ MODAL: RFID & Scanning ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-rfid">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('rfid')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2>RFID &amp; Scanning</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Genom att implementera RFID längs hela värdekedjan kan du eliminera administrativa fel, reducera svinn med upp till 40% och få realtidskontroll på varje enskild artikel.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">By implementing RFID along the entire value chain you can eliminate administrative errors, reduce waste by up to 40% and gain real-time control of every single item.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images trio">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/rfid-tags.jpg" alt="RFID tags" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>rfid-tags.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap contain"><img src="/images/services/rfid-handheld.jpg" alt="Handheld RFID scanner" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>rfid-handheld.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap contain"><img src="/images/services/rfid-warehouse.jpg" alt="Warehouse RFID tunnel" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>rfid-warehouse.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">RFID-taggar på alla produkter</strong><strong class="en-text">RFID tags on all products</strong><span class="sv-text">Tagga varor i hela värdekedjan. Läs av upp till 8 meters räckvidd utan siktlinje – oavsett förpackning.</span><span class="en-text">Tag products throughout the value chain. Read up to 8 metres range without line of sight – regardless of packaging.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Handhållna skannrar</strong><strong class="en-text">Handheld scanners</strong><span class="sv-text">Används för varumottagning, inventeringar och stickprov i butik. Snabbt, korrekt och mobilt.</span><span class="en-text">Used for goods receiving, stocktaking and spot checks in store. Fast, accurate and mobile.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Butiksportar och grindar</strong><strong class="en-text">Shop gates and portals</strong><span class="sv-text">Kontrollera svinnet vid utgången – dubbelrollen som stöldskydd och logistikverktyg ger omedelbar ROI.</span><span class="en-text">Control shrinkage at the exit – the dual role as theft prevention and logistics tool delivers immediate ROI.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Lagertunnlar</strong><strong class="en-text">Warehouse tunnels</strong><span class="sv-text">Scanna en hel lastpall på sekunder. Dramatisk tidsvinst vid in- och utleverans.</span><span class="en-text">Scan an entire pallet in seconds. Dramatic time savings during inbound and outbound deliveries.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Systemintegration</strong><strong class="en-text">System integration</strong><span class="sv-text">RFID-data kopplas mot ERP, POS och WMS för fullständig spårbarhet och automatiska påfyllnadsregler.</span><span class="en-text">RFID data connects to ERP, POS and WMS for full traceability and automatic replenishment rules.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Skalbart och framtidsäkert</strong><strong class="en-text">Scalable and future-proof</strong><span class="sv-text">Starta med ett lager eller en butik – skala upp i din takt. Tekniken är beprovad och mogen.</span><span class="en-text">Start with one warehouse or one store – scale up at your own pace. The technology is proven and mature.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">upp till 40%</strong><strong class="en-text">up to 40%</strong><span class="sv-text">minskat admin-svinn</span><span class="en-text">reduced admin waste</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>8 m</strong><span class="sv-text">läsräckvidd</span><span class="en-text">read range</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Snabb ROI</strong><strong class="en-text">Fast ROI</strong><span class="sv-text">beprovad teknik</span><span class="en-text">proven technology</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ MODAL: Digital Pricing ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-digital-prissattning">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('digital-prissattning')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2><span class="sv-text">Digital prissättning</span><span class="en-text">Digital Pricing</span></h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Prisutvecklingen går allt snabbare och gränsen mellan fysisk och digital handel suddas ut. Elektroniska hyllkantsetiketter och smart prismjukvara ger dig full kontroll – i realtid.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">The pace of price changes is accelerating and the boundary between physical and digital commerce is blurring. Electronic shelf labels and smart pricing software give you full control – in real time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall contain dark-bg"><img src="/images/services/esl-shelf.jpg" alt="Electronic shelf labels" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>esl-shelf.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/pricing-dashboard.jpg" alt="Pricing software dashboard" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>pricing-dashboard.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Elektroniska hyllkantsetiketter (ESL)</strong><strong class="en-text">Electronic Shelf Labels (ESL)</strong><span class="sv-text">Uppdatera tusentals priser med ett knapptryck. Eliminera felprismärkning och manuellt arbete.</span><span class="en-text">Update thousands of prices at the touch of a button. Eliminate pricing errors and manual work.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Fyra etikettsformat</strong><strong class="en-text">Four label formats</strong><span class="sv-text">Hook clip, Shelf clip, Product present och XL – rätt format för varje exponeringstyp och produktvärde.</span><span class="en-text">Hook clip, Shelf clip, Product present and XL – the right format for every display type and product value.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Konkurrentövervakning</strong><strong class="en-text">Competitor monitoring</strong><span class="sv-text">Bevaka omvärldens priser automatiskt och reagera proaktivt utan manuell research.</span><span class="en-text">Automatically monitor competitor pricing and react proactively without manual research.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Regelbaserad prissättning</strong><strong class="en-text">Rule-based pricing</strong><span class="sv-text">Bygg upp smarta prisregler som hanterar marginal, volym och kategori – helt automatiskt.</span><span class="en-text">Build smart pricing rules that handle margin, volume and category – fully automatically.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Stegvis implementering</strong><strong class="en-text">Phased implementation</strong><span class="sv-text">Starta manuellt för att lära dig mekanismerna. Lägg till semi- och helautomatik i din takt.</span><span class="en-text">Start manually to learn the mechanics. Add semi- and full automation at your own pace.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Bred teknologiintegration</strong><strong class="en-text">Broad technology integration</strong><span class="sv-text">Vi har erfarenhet av de flesta plattformar och hjälper dig välja rätt partner för din bransch.</span><span class="en-text">We have experience of most platforms and help you choose the right partner for your industry.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Realtid</strong><strong class="en-text">Real-time</strong><span class="sv-text">prisuppdateringar</span><span class="en-text">price updates</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Noll fel</strong><strong class="en-text">Zero errors</strong><span class="sv-text">i prismärkning</span><span class="en-text">in pricing</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Skalbar</strong><strong class="en-text">Scalable</strong><span class="sv-text">implementering</span><span class="en-text">implementation</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ MODAL: Kiosk & Self-Service ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-kiosk">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('kiosk')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2>Kiosk &amp; Self-Service</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Effektiviseringar i kassamiljön behöver inte ske på bekostnad av kundupplevelsen – det kan vara tvärtom. Vi har byggt lösningar där kunderna väljer obetjänad kassa för att de föredrar flexibiliteten.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">Efficiency improvements at checkout don't have to come at the expense of customer experience. We have built solutions where customers prefer the unmanned checkout for the flexibility it offers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images trio">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/kiosk-app.jpg" alt="Self-checkout app" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>kiosk-app.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/kiosk-tablet.jpg" alt="Tablet POS" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>kiosk-tablet.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall contain"><img src="/images/services/kiosk-cabinet.jpg" alt="All-in-one kiosk cabinet" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>kiosk-cabinet.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">App-baserad scanning</strong><strong class="en-text">App-based scanning</strong><span class="sv-text">Låt kunden använda sin egen smartphone. Minimal hårdvarukostnad och maximal flexibilitet.</span><span class="en-text">Let customers use their own smartphone. Minimal hardware cost and maximum flexibility.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Surfplatta-POS</strong><strong class="en-text">Tablet POS</strong><span class="sv-text">iPad eller Android-surfplatta med standardkomponenter – snabb implementering, låg investering.</span><span class="en-text">iPad or Android tablet with standard components – fast implementation, low investment.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">All-in-one lösningar</strong><strong class="en-text">All-in-one solutions</strong><span class="sv-text">Industristandardkabinett för butiker som vill ha en robust, skalbar och välbeprovad plattform.</span><span class="en-text">Industry-standard cabinet for stores wanting a robust, scalable and well-proven platform.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Informationskiosker med POS</strong><strong class="en-text">Information kiosks with POS</strong><span class="sv-text">Kombinera produktinfo, självscanning och betalning i en enda kontaktpunkt mitt i butiken.</span><span class="en-text">Combine product information, self-scanning and payment in a single touchpoint in the store.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kundresan i fokus</strong><strong class="en-text">Customer journey focus</strong><span class="sv-text">Vi designar lösningar som är intuitiva och enkla att adoptera – för alla kundgrupper.</span><span class="en-text">We design solutions that are intuitive and easy to adopt – for all customer groups.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Win-win för butik och kund</strong><strong class="en-text">Win-win for store and customer</strong><span class="sv-text">Lägre personalkostnader vid toppar, kortare köer och en upplevelse kunderna faktiskt uppskattar.</span><span class="en-text">Lower staff costs at peak times, shorter queues and an experience customers actually appreciate.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Kortare köer</strong><strong class="en-text">Shorter queues</strong><span class="sv-text">nöjdare kunder</span><span class="en-text">happier customers</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Lägre kostnad</strong><strong class="en-text">Lower cost</strong><span class="sv-text">per transaktion</span><span class="en-text">per transaction</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4</strong><span class="sv-text">format att välja</span><span class="en-text">formats available</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ MODAL: NPS & Customer Analytics ═══ -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-nps-analytics">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('nps-analytics')" aria-label="Stäng">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi &amp; System</span><span class="en-text">Technology &amp; Systems</span></p>
      <h2>NPS &amp; Customer Analytics</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Vi har arbetat med kundnöjdhetsmätningar i över 20 år och är fortfarande förvånade över företag som inte systematiskt samlar in och agerar på kundfeedback.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">We have worked with customer satisfaction measurement for over 20 years and are still surprised by companies that do not systematically collect and act on customer feedback.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/nps-feedback-app.jpg" alt="Feedback App" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>nps-feedback-app.jpg</span></div>'" /></div>
